    "body": "I've been trying to implement this but I can't figure out how to get the path to the project file. There is a window.folders(), but I don't think that will be enough. For example, if I had multiple folders specified in my project file, but I want to specify a relative include path, how do I pick which folder to be relative to?\r\n\r\nAny ideas?\r\n\r\nI guess for right now I could just pick the first element in windows.folders() and just use that."
